snippet.title: Celebrating 10 years of EUIV
snippet.description:
For ten years, the masters of historical grand strategy have been designing and improving the grandest of games. Originally released in August 2013, Europa Universalis IV has opened a window into the past, challenging players to rewrite the history of the early modern world, taking them from Renaissance to Revolution as any nation or culture in the world. This video timeline celebrates EUIV and you - It's lively community. Thank you for playing all along the way!
